{"tid":217531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲仔多次非法肛交 父嬲爆報警拉人","createTime":"2017-04-26T00:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T23:13:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96abb9e8de018a98adbb4ec97a8585edf64d8d6f","tid":217531,"uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:12:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>16歲仔多次非法肛交 父嬲爆報警拉人</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-04-26 05:21:00 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n深水埗警方調查案件。<br />\n凌晨1時許，長沙灣福榮街一名43男子報案，指其16歲兒子與一名39歲男子，自2014年7月至今年4月期間，於深水埗區一單位及公廁懷疑作出多次同性肛交。<br />\n<br />\n警員經初步調查後，於深水埗區拘捕該名39歲男子，涉嫌「與16歲以下男子作出同性肛交」，現正被扣留調查，案件交深水埗警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。"},{"pid":"bec0c22b559f5fbb7a3e23ab2753d2db44f2ac6f","tid":217531,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab754f6ec7dcffffbc094810f83c9d48ec6a52b2","tid":217531,"uid":63925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:14:08.000Z","msg":"個老豆點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f740611ede6b74fae6d5116b03097692ad098274","tid":217531,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個老豆點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big